import React from 'react'
import { Box, Button,TextField, Typography } from '@mui/material'

const Contacts = () => {
  
  return (

    <Box style={{textAlign:"center"}}>
<Typography
        variant="h3"
        sx={{ fontSize: "30px", fontWeight: "bold", color: "#000339", my: 2, marginBottom:"40px" }}
      >
        Feel Free To Contact
      </Typography>
  <form 
  action="https://formspree.io/f/xgedgjkr"
  method="POST" >
<Box style={{justifyContent:"center"}}>
<TextField id="outlined-basic" label="Name" variant='outlined' style={{textAlign:"center", width:"30%"}}/>
</Box>
<Box>
<TextField id="outlined-basic" label="Email" variant='outlined' style={{textAlign:"center", width:"30%", marginTop:"10px"}}/>
</Box>
<TextField id="outlined-multiline-flexible" label="Mass" multiline maxRows={4} />
<Button variant='contained' style={{marginTop:"10px"}}>SUBMIT</Button>
</form>
</Box>
  );
}

export default Contacts
